{"word":"G4448 - πυρόω - pyróō - poo-ro'-o - Burn","slug":"G4448","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πυρόω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>pyróō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>poo-ro'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Burn"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C0;&#x03C5;&#x03C1;&#x03BF;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - puroo&#x0304;</b> - <i>poo-ro'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G4442\">G4442</a>; to <i>kindle</i>, that is, (passively) to <i>be ignited</i>, <i>glow</i> (literally), <i>be refined</i> (by implication), or (figuratively) to <i>be inflamed</i> (with anger, grief, lust): - burn, fiery, be on fire, try."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G4442\">G4442</a>, <a href=\"#/G4443\">G4443</a>, <a href=\"#/G4447\">G4447</a>, <a href=\"#/G4449\">G4449</a>, <a href=\"#/G4450\">G4450</a>, <a href=\"#/G4451\">G4451</a>"}]}